<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <title>Next PATCO <%= @theStation.present? ? "&mdash; #{@theStation}".html_safe : '' %></title>
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1, maximum-scale=1" />
  <link id="favicon" rel="shortcut icon" href="/train-circle.png" type="image/png" />
  <link rel="apple-touch-icon" href="/train-circle.png">

  <meta property="og:title" content="Next PATCO" />
  <meta property="og:url" content="http://nextpat.co" />
  <meta property="og:description" content="An interactive site for exploring the schedule for the PATCO High Speed Line between South Jersey and Center City Philadelphia." />
  <meta property="og:image" content="http://np-dev.nextpat.co/assets/train-circle.png" />
  <meta property="og:type" content="website" />

  <%= stylesheet_link_tag    "application", :media => "all" %>
  <%= javascript_include_tag "application" %>
  <%= csrf_meta_tags %>
</head>
<body>

  <header>
    <a href="/"><%= image_tag("train-circle.png", :class => "site-logo") %></a>
    <h2 style="text-align: center;">NEXT PATCO</h2>
  </header>

  <h3 style="text-align: center; font-style: italic;">Holiday Schedule!</h3>
  <p style="text-align: center; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1.35;">PATCO will have a holiday schedule in effect for November 26-28:<br/> <a href="http://ridepatco.org/publish/library/11-26-14%20Wed%20Early%20out%20Sign.pdf" target="_blank">26th</a>, <a href="http://ridepatco.org/publish/library/2014%20Thanksgiving%20Day%20Sched%20Sign.pdf" target="_blank">27th</a>, <a href="http://ridepatco.org/publish/library/11%2028%2014%20Friday%20Sch.pdf" target="_blank">28th</a>.
  
   <br /><br /> As always, your best bet is to follow <a href="http://twitter.com/PatcoWatchers" target="_blank">@PATCOWatchers</a> and <a href="http://twitter.com/RIDEPatco" target="_blank">@RidePATCO</a> on Twitter for the latest information.</p>

  <br />
  
  <%= yield %>

